➜江西诗人时差先生：空中大道
http://www.sohu.com/a/422613778_100115135	36958
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201004/ff1d1a7817a84a4eaac6529b20edd62e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>空中大道</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/时差先生</strong> </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你有茶，有酒，我有肉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">深呼吸，做一次跪拜运动</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">檀香释放的味</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">安神，排毒，透性</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">静坐，听韵，颂经</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以善为念，立信为本</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">莫悲哀，勿生气，筑善根</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">能容小人为大人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">积善成德，方能自得</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">白日莫虚度，青春不再来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">勤能补拙，俭以养廉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">读心经，皈依道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">凡世界，一为首</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">复本还原，归一归空</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201004/3b08bc5029734cf4a8318502937a47b5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
