➜广西诗人陈熠明：遥远了岁月的乡愁
http://www.sohu.com/a/422616204_100115135	37951
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201004/e521a555b6ae44739cd640be9d9f0972.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>遥远了岁月的乡愁</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>现代诗原创作品·心灵诗幻陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(一)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">回到这一个山乡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">回到这一个久别了岁月的山乡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一阵风走过</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一阵风轻轻地走过</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">走过我这一个</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">遥遥远远地别去了岁月的身旁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>屋檐下的燕子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>依旧还是双双对对地歌唱</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">歌唱着山乡里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一心眷恋了泥土的芬芳</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>儿时喜戏的池塘</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>在父母的呼唤里荡漾</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">荡漾起那一群</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不停地热闹了时光的儿郎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(二)</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
