<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>回到这一个村庄</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>回到这一个久别了流年的村庄</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一只狗走过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一只狗悄悄地走过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>走过我这一个</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>长长久久地别去了流年的身旁</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">竹林下的河水</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">依旧还是清清楚楚地流淌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>流淌着村庄里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一心追寻着梦想的希望</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">儿时藏隐的荷塘</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在父母的催促里回荡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>回荡起那一群</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不停地大闹了时光的儿郎</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(三)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一颗心很羡慕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">羡慕山里鹰那一双丰满了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>丰满了希望</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>和丰满了梦想的翅膀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">山里鹰在高天上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来来来回回地飞翔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>飞翔出那一个</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>自由于自己的梦想</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">山里鹰的心思</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">山里鹰的心思是专一的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>专一着生养他的山乡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>同时也专一着温暖了他的太阳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">山里鹰飞得再高</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可他还是舍不得飞出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>飞出这一个</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>宁静了岁月的山乡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天涯里那一片</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云霞还在远远飘荡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>飘荡着故乡想我</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>和飘荡着我想故乡的眼光</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201004/e9f9dfa2e73844d2a3e62a09ba7f6af4.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(四)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一颗心很羡慕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">羡慕山里鹰那一双锐利了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>锐利了追寻</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>和锐利了向往的目光</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">山里鹰在山巅上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">坦坦荡荡地飞翔出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>飞翔出那一个</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>浪漫于自己的梦想</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">山里鹰的心思</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">山里鹰的心思是眷恋的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>眷恋着偏爱他的山乡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>同时也眷恋着历练了他的太阳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">山里鹰飞得再远</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可他还是舍不得飞出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>飞出这一个</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>和谐了时光的山乡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天涯里那一片</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">夕阳还在不舍地回望</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>回望着高山想我</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>和回望着我想高山的眼光</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(五)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">眷恋着山乡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一阵风的过往</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我的心脏里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>就会清清楚楚地听见</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">听见我父亲的骨节</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在风雨的交加里弯弯曲曲地断裂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>断裂着他那一生的艰辛</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>和断裂着他那一生的匆忙</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">父亲是我生命里的高山</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我亲眼看见艰苦的劳作崛起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>崛起父亲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一心淹没了风雨的坚强</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">父亲是我生活里的榜样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我亲眼看见坎坷的路途上走出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>走出父亲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一心苦涩了岁月的漫长</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">父亲的心很温暖</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">温暖得像高山上那一个坦荡了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>坦荡了遥远的时空</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>和坦荡了高尚的太阳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(六)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梦幻着山乡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一河水的流淌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我的心眼里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>就会明明白白地看见</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看见我母亲的心血</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在清澈的小河里曲曲折折地流淌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>流淌着她那一生的善良</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>和流淌着他那一生的繁忙</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">母亲是我生命里的月亮</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我亲眼看见流汗的劳作撑起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>撑起母亲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一心沉重了时光的渴望</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">母亲是我成长里的榜样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我亲眼看见干枯的果园里开出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>开出母亲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一心喜悦了季节的芬芳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">母亲的心很善良</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">善良得像高天上那一个明朗了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>明朗了黑暗的远方</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>和明朗了长夜的月亮</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201004/1c41c048c53a4e21831846471d982420.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(七)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青藤爬满了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">思念的篱笆墙</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>撒开着他那一张</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>可以笼罩着渴望的情网</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在村边的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小河里来来回回地打捞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>打捞起</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>消沉在岁月里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一心落漠了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">徘徊和落漠了迷茫的梦想</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(八)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>悬挂在枝头的思量</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>在清风的嘱咐里辗辗转转地飘落</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">飘落了他</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">痴心里那无尽的相思</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>还要飘落了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>他情怀里那无尽的彷徨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">遮不住别离的眼泪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在那一场梦里冰冰凉凉地潮湿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>潮湿起回眸里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一个久别了岁月的山乡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(九)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">流水拉长了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">思念的月亮湾</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>甩开着他那一把</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>可以收割着希望的刀郎</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在村边的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">田野上来来回回地收藏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>收藏起</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>成熟在季节里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一片喜悦了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">心情和喜悦了希望的梦想</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201004/c83b8ffa095a469a95031b4b32efb221.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>晾晒在村头的云霞</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>在流水的嘱咐里遥遥远远地飘荡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">飘荡了他</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">痴情里那缠绵的等望</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>还要飘荡了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>他胸怀里那缠绵的向往</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">遮不住别离的惆怅</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在那一场梦里隐隐约约地疼痛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>疼痛起记忆里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一个久别了流年的村庄</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(十一)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看看远处那一座座</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看看远处那一座座云雾的青山</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我的眼里啊</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>就闪过了我的父老</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">掠过了我父老</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那每一双扛起了生计的肩膀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>记忆里我</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>清清楚楚地记得</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>记得那每一双肩膀是在扛起</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">扛起东方里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一心充满了希望的太阳</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十二)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>看看眼前这一个个</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>看看眼前着一个个古老的瓦房</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我的眼里啊</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就掠过了我的父老</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>掠过了我父老</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那每一脸劳苦了岁月的脸庞</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">记忆里我</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">苦苦涩涩地记得</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">记得那每一张脸庞是在仰望</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>仰望长夜里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一心充满了和谐的月亮</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201004/f9b87186964041a7b72b5167d70323e1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(十三)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">遥望天涯那一弯弯</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">遥望天涯那一弯弯祥和的月亮</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我的眼里啊</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>就浮现了我的母亲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">浮现了我母亲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那每一张干枯了春华的脸庞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>记忆里我</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>酸酸楚楚地记得</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>记得那每一丝笑脸是在撑起</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">撑起长夜里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一心装满了慈祥的月亮</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十四)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>难舍眼前这一暮暮</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>难舍眼前着一暮暮西沉的残阳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我的眼里啊</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就飘过了我的父亲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>飘过了我父亲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那每一双酸涩了流年的眼光</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">记忆里我</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">坦坦荡荡地记得</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">记得那每一力肩膀是在挑起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>挑起清晨里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一心装满了沉重的太阳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(十五)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">村边的小河</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在静静地流淌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>流淌进爷爷</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>讲给我的故事里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">故事里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有我童年的渴望</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>故事里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>还有着我少年的向往</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小河依然流淌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">流淌出村头那一个萌动了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>萌动了追寻</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>和萌动了诗幻的远方</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201004/3e3931e5b126475e9c24e7085adcf51a.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">﻿</span></strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(十六)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">记忆的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">泪水里充满了怀想</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>怀想着我</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一个宁静了牵挂的山乡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乡愁渐渐地明朗了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>明朗在月色里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我那一个平安了时光的梦乡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乡愁渐渐地眷恋了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>眷恋在别离里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我那一首浪漫了天涯的诗行</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(十七)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">村庄的炊烟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在柔柔地飘荡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>飘荡进奶奶</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>说给我的传说里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">传说里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有着我童年的梦乡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>传说里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>还有着我少年的梦想</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小河依然流淌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">流淌出村头那一个萌动了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>萌动了追寻</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>和萌动了诗幻的远方</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(十八)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">记忆的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">心血里充满了滚烫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>滚烫着我</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一个漫长了思念的村庄</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乡愁渐渐地清晰了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>清晰在岁月里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我那一个斑斓了生命的梦乡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乡愁渐渐地模煳了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>模煳在流年里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我那一眼潮湿了天涯的泪光</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201004/fe1627a3f65d48c99f4e698e25da59b3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>陈熠明，笔名心灵诗幻，男，1976年生，广西平果市人。爱好文学创作，曾有诗歌作品发布于多家报刊杂志和网络。时任星连文学社副社长。职业于中医，热衷于传统文化传播。诗是文笔与文笔的向往，诗是朋友与朋友的交心。诗是千难和万险的将来，诗是岁月与年华的渴望。诗是春夏和秋冬的风景，诗是父亲和母亲的嘱咐，诗是父亲和母亲的叮咛。诗是渡船与碧波的远航，诗是生命与大海的彼岸。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201004/a9379dcd23dc43178588513916100a9c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>❖星连文学社管理团队：</strong></p>
<p>★ <strong>名誉社长:</strong>叶仲录 ☆<strong>总顾问:</strong>薛依云 ☆<strong>首席顾问:</strong>欧大象 ☆<strong>执行顾问:</strong>岩心（薛莹） ☆<strong>顾问团成员:</strong>欧大象（文光）、岩心（薛莹）、石秉旺、陈文化、高原红、碧海（陈碧珍)、黄香玉 ☆<strong>社长兼总编:</strong>星连 ☆<strong>常务副社长:</strong>岩心（薛莹） ☆<strong>副社长:</strong>丁冬亮、绝尘道长、梁继权、高晓园、陈熠明、东晓 、木子 ☆<strong>艺术总监:</strong>陆廷教 ☆<strong>编委会主任:</strong>听尘居士 ☆<strong>编委会成员:</strong>孤客、黄香玉、星连、枫叶、绮雯、徐玉兰、叶仲录、薛依云、高晓园、田书芹、木子……（添加中） ☆<strong>主编:</strong>游散居士 ☆<strong>副主编：</strong> 丁冬亮、闫加辉、张立标、张君霞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201004/b855299b2bcd4c3e9e4fc54f43497c8f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201004/6db8f4bd3fe340adaba92a80d7e3f7f4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>❖主编简介：</strong></p>
<p>▲笔名：星连、星连193，原名：卢链生，号游散居士，别号：中原听真，男，汉族，七零后，籍贯：广东汕尾，现居深圳。系中国诗联协会理事，中国诗词协会会员，世界汉诗协会会员，中国网络诗歌学会会员，河北采风学会会员，中原诗词研究会会员，太行诗词协会会员，认证诗人，网站签约作家。2014年受江西电台连线采访，作品散发各大网站及入选各类诗集、文集等，诗歌及其他作品曾获特等奖、一等奖、二等奖、铜奖、优秀奖各类奖项。主要结集作品有：诗集《爱情与人生》，长篇小说《漂泊》、《江湖客传》、《都市迷情之情仇恩怨》，小说集《百味人生》以及散文集等。</p>
